<div id="patternMainContents">
<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="Page_Caching">  Page Caching </h1>
How to get the best from HTML Caching.
<p></p>

<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"><span class="foswikiTocTitle">On this page:</span> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Using_the_Cache"> Using the Cache </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Cache_Expiry"> Cache Expiry </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Loading_parts_of_a_page_asynchronously"> Loading parts of a page asynchronously </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Dirty_Areas"> Dirty Areas </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Controlling_which_pages_to_cache_and_which_ones_not"> Controlling which pages to cache and which ones not </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Refreshing_the_cache"> Refreshing the cache </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Command_line_cache_refresh"> Command line cache refresh </a>
</li></ul> 
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Caching_SEARCH_results"> Caching SEARCH results </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Caching_REST_results_40Developers_41"> Caching REST results (Developers) </a>
</li></ul> 
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Configuring_the_Cache"> Configuring the Cache </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Choosing_a_database_engine"> Choosing a database engine </a> <ul>
